{"type":null,"faqId":48247,"title":"Mate S插入降噪耳机，充电指示灯过一会灭了怎么办？","answer":"您好，降噪耳机指示灯一共三种状态：\n红灯：充电\n绿灯：开降噪\n黄灯：充电+开降噪（红灯和绿灯均亮，两种光叠加呈现黄色）\n不亮：不充电不开降噪。\n插入降噪耳机后，过一会灭了，属正常情况，因为电量充满以后，会停充，这时充电指示灯红灯由亮变灭。\n另：因为手机给降噪耳机充电是通过MIC脚，所以MIC录音与充电功能不能同时有效，当用到耳机MIC录音的场景时，充电指示灯也会由亮变灭。","faqTypeId":144,"faqType":"其他","useful":0,"unUseful":0,"languageId":2,"languageName":"zh_cn","faqCode":"3913","faqTypeCode":"Handsets-Others","isTop":"0","moduleCode":"faq","productId":null,"productCode":null,"postDate":1447062556000,"seriesProductName":"CRR-CL10,CRR-TL10,CRR-UL10","visitedTimes":35,"isUsefulFlag":null,"score":0,"times":0,"imageList":null,"displayType":"text","justView":"0","fileName":null,"filePath":null,"imagePath":null,"imageName":null,"productIdList":null,"curPage":null,"pageSize":null,"siteCode":null,"statusFlag":"Publish","returnCode":0,"totalRows":null,"keywords":null,"avgScore":0.0,"createDate":null,"totalPages":null}